sentence: Robots can be autonomous or semi-autonomous and range from humanoids such as Honda ' s Advanced Step in Innovative Mobility (ASIMO) and TOSY ' s TOSY Ping Pong Playing Robot (TOPIO) to industrial robot s, medical operating robot s, patient assist robots, dog therapy robots, collectively programmed swarm robots, UAV drones such as General Atomics MQ-1 Predator, and even microscopic nano robots.
